<li id="cite_note-isbn0-19-530424-1-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-isbn0-19-530424-1_5-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFTushnet.2C_Mark_V.2007">Tushnet, Mark V. (2007). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=81aeiboJfbkC&amp;pg=PR15&amp;dq=Tushnet+%2B+%22blowing+smoke%22#PPR16,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=81aeiboJfbkC&amp;pg=PR15&amp;dq=Tushnet+%2B+%22blowing+smoke%22#PPR16,M1" rel="nofollow">Out of range: why the Constitution can't end the battle over guns</a></i>. Oxford [Oxfordshire]: Oxford University Press. pp.&#160;xv. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195304241" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-530424-1</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=81aeiboJfbkC&amp;pg=PR15&amp;dq=Tushnet+%2B+%22blowing+smoke%22#PPR16,M1" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=81aeiboJfbkC&amp;pg=PR15&amp;dq=Tushnet+%2B+%22blowing+smoke%22#PPR16,M1" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=81aeiboJfbkC&amp;pg=PR15&amp;dq=Tushnet+%2B+%22blowing+smoke%22#PPR16,M1</a></span>.  "As with many constitutional provisions, there's no definitive answer to what the Second Amendment means."</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Out+of+range%3A+why+the+Constitution+can%27t+end+the+battle+over+guns&amp;rft.aulast=Tushnet%2C+Mark+V.&amp;rft.au=Tushnet%2C+Mark+V.&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3Bxv&amp;rft.place=Oxford+%5BOxfordshire%5D&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-19-530424-1&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D81aeiboJfbkC%26pg%3DPR15%26dq%3DTushnet%2B%252B%2B%2522blowing%2Bsmoke%2522%23PPR16%2CM1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Second_Amendment_to_the_United_States_Constitution"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
