<li id="cite_note-130"><b><a href="#cite_ref-130" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFJoan_Biskupic_and_Kevin_Johnson2008">Joan Biskupic and Kevin Johnson (2008-06-27). <a href="http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm" rel="nofollow">"Landmark ruling fires challenges to gun laws"</a>. USA Today<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.usatoday.com/news/washington/2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-01-05</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Landmark+ruling+fires+challenges+to+gun+laws&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Joan+Biskupic+and+Kevin+Johnson&amp;rft.au=Joan+Biskupic+and+Kevin+Johnson&amp;rft.date=2008-06-27&amp;rft.pub=USA+Today&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fnews%2Fwashington%2F2008-06-26-scotus-guns_N.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Second_Amendment_to_the_United_States_Constitution"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
